rubric.description:
Students will

* Scrub and clean up data
* Run several unsupervised learning methods: k-means,k-median, neural gas to segment the data
* Visualize the clusters

This project is part of the Predictive Analytics for Business Nanodegree program.

Student Instructions

After completing the project by filling out the submission template and reviewing it using the [project rubric](https://review.udacity.com/#!/rubrics/424/view), click the Submit Project button below and upload your submission.

You may also include your Alteryx workflow if you'd like. If your submission does not meet specifications, having the workflow may help the review identify mistakes.
